snippet.title: CHIGUN Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Get CHIGUN Here! http://alexvscoding.itch.io/chigun

CHIGUN is a cockfight with guns, pitting a pair of pistol wielding chickens against each other. 
Peck up bullets throughout the level and ricochet them off blocks to blast your poultry opponent to pieces. 

Development Log: http://forums.tigsource.com/index.php?topic=41984.0

Latest Development News on Twitter - @alexvscoding
